query:
SELECT 
  wb.id,
  wb.branchId,
  b.name as branch_name,
  wb.weekNumber,
  wb.month,
  wb.year,
  wb.totalAmount,
  wb.status,
  wb.weekStart,
  wb.weekEnd
FROM weeklyBonuses wb
JOIN branches b ON wb.branchId = b.id
WHERE b.name LIKE '%طويق%'
ORDER BY wb.year DESC, wb.month DESC, wb.weekNumber DESC
LIMIT 20;
